items.headline: Welcome to Dino Dominion Wiki!
items.desc:
Dino Dominion is an app for Iphone and Android-based devices.  The game style is similar to other card-based apps, but unlike these other apps there are a few extra elements to Dino Dominion that make it different.  The main plot behind Dino Dominion is that you work for a company (players can choose between either Laurasia or Gondwana) that is exploring Isla Dormir, an island where Dinosaurs still exist. 

If you're a fan, join us today to share your knowledge and passion with your fellow players. After all, this is a community site that anyone can edit, including you!
